---
name:            test_shl_big_scalar
body:             |
  bb.0.entry:
    ; There are two cases to consider:
    ; 1) If the shift amount is >= 32-bit, the lower bits of the source are 
    ;    shifted completely into the higher bits of the result (using an 
    ;    adjusted shift amount, ADJ_AMT), while the lower bits of the result are 
    ;    0.
    ; 2) If the shift amount is < 32, both the lower bits and the upper bits of
    ;    the src are shifted by the same amount, however parts of the lower bits
    ;    might be shifted into the higher part. Thus, the lower src part is 
    ;    additionally shifted right (by D4RIGHTSHAMT) and OR'ed to the
    ;    left-shifted src high part.
    ; CHECK-LABEL: name: test_shl_big_scalar
    ; CHECK: [[E4:%[0-9]+]]:_(s64) = COPY $e4
    ; CHECK: [[E6:%[0-9]+]]:_(s64) = COPY $e6
    ; CHECK: [[AMT:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_TRUNC [[E6]]
    ; CHECK: [[THIRTYTWO:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_CONSTANT i32 32
    ; CHECK: [[D4:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32), [[D5:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_UNMERGE_VALUES [[E4]](s64)
    ; CHECK: [[ADJ_AMT:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_SUB [[AMT]], [[THIRTYTWO]]
    ; CHECK: [[D4RIGHTSHAMT:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_SUB [[THIRTYTWO]], [[AMT]]
    ; CHECK: [[ZERO:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_CONSTANT i32 0
    ; CHECK: [[CMP:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_ICMP intpred(ult), [[AMT]](s32), [[THIRTYTWO]]
    ; CHECK: [[LESS32BIT:%[0-9]+]]:_(s1) = G_TRUNC [[CMP]](s32)
    ; CHECK: [[ISZERO:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_ICMP intpred(eq), [[AMT]](s32), [[ZERO]]
    ; CHECK: [[ISZERORES:%[0-9]+]]:_(s1) = G_TRUNC [[ISZERO]](s32)
    ; CHECK: [[D4SHL:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_SHL [[D4]], [[AMT]]
    ; CHECK: [[LSHR:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_LSHR [[D4]], [[D4RIGHTSHAMT]]
    ; CHECK: [[D5SHL:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_SHL [[D5]], [[AMT]]
    ; CHECK: [[OR:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_OR [[LSHR]], [[D5SHL]]
    ; CHECK: [[ZERO_2:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_CONSTANT i32 0
    ; CHECK: [[LOWER2UPPER:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_SHL [[D4]], [[ADJ_AMT]]
    ; CHECK: [[LOWER:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_SELECT [[LESS32BIT]](s1), [[D4SHL]], [[ZERO_2]]
    ; CHECK: [[D5RES:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_SELECT [[LESS32BIT]](s1), [[OR]], [[LOWER2UPPER]]
    ; CHECK: [[UPPER:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_SELECT [[ISZERORES]](s1), [[D5]], [[D5RES]]
    ; CHECK: [[RES:%[0-9]+]]:_(s64) = G_MERGE_VALUES [[LOWER]](s32), [[UPPER]](s32)
    ; CHECK: $e2 = COPY [[RES]](s64)
   %0:_(s64) = COPY $e4
   %1:_(s64) = COPY $e6
   %2:_(s64) = G_SHL %0, %1
   $e2 = COPY %2(s64)
...
---
name:            test_shl_cimm_32
body:             |
  bb.1:
    liveins: $d4
    ; CHECK-LABEL: name: test_shl_cimm_32
    ; CHECK: [[COPY:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = COPY $d4
    ; CHECK: [[C:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_CONSTANT i32 8
    ; CHECK: [[SHL:%[0-9]+]]:_(s32) = G_SHL [[COPY]], [[C]](s32)
    ; CHECK: $d2 = COPY [[SHL]](s32)
    %0:_(s32) = COPY $d4
    %1:_(s32) = G_CONSTANT i32 8
    %2:_(s32) = G_SHL %0, %1(s32)
    $d2 = COPY %2(s32)
...
